          strong DoubleCheck helps you make less.
      section#Horatio.section.section--menu
        h2.section__title Check it out bru
        span.link-copy

      section.section
      section.content.content--related
        h1 Thanks for visiting
        i.fa.fa-hand-peace-o.fa-2x(style='color:white')
